  <li>
    <p>Young great ladies <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="have great penetration in such matters; penetration - 洞察力"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(对这些事情总是非常敏锐)</code></b> as these.</p>
